BT 0 g /F2 18 Tf 241.2 740 Td (WHAT IS TRAUMA?) Tj ET
q 0.5 G 1 w 72 730 m 540 730 l S Q
BT 0.2 g /F2 11 Tf 72 700 Td (Trauma is what happens INSIDE you after something bad happens.) Tj ET
BT 0.2 g /F1 11 Tf 72 678 Td (It's not about what happened being 'bad enough.' If it affected you, it counts.) Tj ET
BT 0.2 g /F1 11 Tf 72 648 Td (Trauma can come from:) Tj ET
BT 0.2 g /F1 11 Tf 90 628 Td (- Abuse \(physical, emotional, sexual\)) Tj ET
BT 0.2 g /F1 11 Tf 90 610 Td (- Neglect or abandonment) Tj ET
BT 0.2 g /F1 11 Tf 90 592 Td (- Bullying or cyberbullying) Tj ET
BT 0.2 g /F1 11 Tf 90 574 Td (- Witnessing violence) Tj ET
BT 0.2 g /F1 11 Tf 90 556 Td (- Loss of someone you love) Tj ET
BT 0.2 g /F1 11 Tf 90 538 Td (- Accidents or medical trauma) Tj ET
BT 0.2 g /F1 11 Tf 90 520 Td (- Natural disasters) Tj ET
BT 0.2 g /F1 11 Tf 90 502 Td (- Community violence) Tj ET
BT 0.2 g /F1 11 Tf 90 484 Td (- Divorce or family chaos) Tj ET
BT 0.2 g /F1 11 Tf 90 466 Td (- Anything that made you feel unsafe or helpless) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F2 11 Tf 72 433 Td (YOUR EXPERIENCE IS VALID. You don't need to compare your pain to others.) Tj ET

endstream
endobj
