q 0.5 G 1 w 72 730 m 540 730 l S Q
BT 0.2 g /F1 11 Tf 72 700 Td (After trauma, your brain gets stuck in 'survival mode.' This causes:) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F2 11 Tf 72 672 Td (BRAIN:) Tj ET
BT 0.2 g /F1 10 Tf 160 672 Td (Trouble concentrating, memory gaps, nightmares, flashbacks) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F2 11 Tf 72 644 Td (BODY:) Tj ET
BT 0.2 g /F1 10 Tf 160 644 Td (Stomachaches, headaches, muscle tension, fatigue, startle response) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F2 11 Tf 72 616 Td (EMOTIONS:) Tj ET
BT 0.2 g /F1 10 Tf 160 616 Td (Anger outbursts, numbness, anxiety, sadness, shame, mood swings) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F2 11 Tf 72 588 Td (BEHAVIOR:) Tj ET
BT 0.2 g /F1 10 Tf 160 588 Td (Isolation, risk-taking, sleep changes, avoiding reminders) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F2 11 Tf 72 560 Td (RELATIONSHIPS:) Tj ET
BT 0.2 g /F1 10 Tf 160 560 Td (Trust issues, pushing people away, people-pleasing) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F2 12 Tf 72 517 Td (IMPORTANT: These are NORMAL responses to ABNORMAL events.) Tj ET
BT 0.2 g /F1 11 Tf 72 495 Td (Your brain is trying to protect you. It just needs help knowing you're safe now.) Tj ET

endstream
endobj
